long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
WhatsApp Contacts is a tools that add extra button to web Whatsapp to get and download all numbers in chat, in group and in contact include they name. With this you can too find group link in google.

You can save a lot of your time and avoiding get customer number errors, and find a new group means finding a new customer.

FEATURES :
✔ Get all numbers from Contacts list
✔ Get all numbers from Chats list
✔ Get all numbers from Groups
✔ Get list of your Groups
✔ Join all Group by your list
✔ One click to download contacts to Excel sheet (.csv) file
✔ Help Find link Group on google.com and ask.com
   - Need manual input first change "keyword" to targeted keyword
   - Change Region in Search Settings to targeted Region/Country
